title: Travis Build Error: Cannot import _C.so file
body_html:
It seems that the _C.*.so shared object file is not being built correctly and this is leading to build errors on Travis.

Running JIT tests
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "test_jit.py", line 1, in <module>
    import torch
  File "/home/travis/virtualenv/python2.7.9/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/__init__.py", line 53, in <module>
    from torch._C import *
ImportError: /home/travis/virtualenv/python2.7.9/lib/python2.7/site-packages/torch/_C.so: undefined symbol: _ZN4thpp8THTensorIcEC1EP13THLongStorageS3_
